main event: Reports of a large flaming object crashing into the jungle in the Philippines.
interesting points: No visual observation was made but a noise impact indicated a possible crash., The incident may involve an ICBM re-entry vehicle., Eyewitnesses likely saw the first dummy warhead during the incident., Confirmation from multiple Air Force sources indicated no aircraft were in the area at the time., Citizens' observations in Mindanao described a flaming object descending on a downward trajectory.
